00:29:52,345 --> 00:29:53,466
What on earth

539
00:29:54,785 --> 00:29:55,545
are you two doing?

540
00:29:56,145 --> 00:29:57,706
One of you not sleeping

541
00:29:58,065 --> 00:29:59,785
and the other acting
like a ghost sleepwalking.

542
00:30:03,946 --> 00:30:05,906
My back hurt,
so I came out to sit for a bit.

543
00:30:06,345 --> 00:30:08,226
How was I supposed to know
he'd be sleepwalking?

544
00:30:12,666 --> 00:30:13,746
Liang Daiwen,

545
00:30:14,105 --> 00:30:14,506
you...

546
00:30:14,825 --> 00:30:15,865
Don't try to give me puppy eyes.

547
00:30:17,105 --> 00:30:19,345
If you make a ruckus
in the middle of night again,

548
00:30:19,946 --> 00:30:21,026
I'll get the aluminum basin

549
00:30:21,266 --> 00:30:21,906
and knock you out.

550
00:30:28,506 --> 00:30:29,785
You pretended to sleepwalk

551
00:30:29,825 --> 00:30:30,986
just to get her attention?

552
00:30:33,226 --> 00:30:33,825
Mdm. Wang,

553
00:30:34,312 --> 00:30:35,944
you told me
that the slow bird had to fly first

554
00:30:36,105 --> 00:30:36,825
this afternoon.

555
00:30:39,625 --> 00:30:40,226
You are dumb.

